SUMMARY:Rogues & Reveals: A Burlesque & Drag tribute to fantasy roleplaying
DESCRIPTION:March 20\, 2026 // Doors 7pm // Show 8pm\nall prices + fees\nBUY TICKETS \n \nHigh in Dexterity and even higher in Charisma\, we’re bringing together a group of natural 20s for a night of burlesque and drag based on fantasy role-playing! Join us for an evening of dashing rogues\, bewitching bards\, and critical hits! \nAccessibility: Masks (KN-95 or higher quality) are required in the venue when not drinking (provided free at the venue). HEPA filters will be in the space\, and a Far UV light will be used for the stage area. Please stay home if you are not feeling well. \nThe main entrance is on the building’s east side and is accessible via a ramp for all patrons. The washrooms are not gender-separated and are located on the lower level\, accessible by lift. The lift requires an attendant to operate it. More access can be found here. For any other questions\, please contact us at info@nerdgirlburlesque.ca. \nPlease contact us in advance at the email above with any concerns\, or approach one of the producers or the door person on the evening\, and we would be happy to assist you. \n19+
URL:https://buddiesinbadtimes.com/event/rogues-reveals-a-burlesque-drag-tribute-to-fantasy-roleplaying/
LOCATION:Tallulahs
END:VEVENT
