SUMMARY:Formless Film Festival
DESCRIPTION:Tuesday\, March 31\, 2026  // 7pm\n$15\nall prices + fees\nBUY TICKETS \n\nJoin us for the inaugural Formless Film Festival\, a special night celebrating trans storytelling\, performance\, and visibility in honour of Trans Day of Visibility presented by Vajayjay Abrams and Fine & Dandi Events. This first-of-its-kind event brings together local and international trans filmmakers and drag artists for an evening of film\, art\, and community. \nHosted by the dazzling Dandi Luv\, the night features an all-trans drag lineup: Steak\, Vyper\, Panic Fantasy\, and El Experimento. \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n\nAlongside the performances\, we’ll be screening a selection of local trans short films: \nParida Por El Mar (Chile) \nUnhappy Sexy Girl (Canada) \nLaneways (Canada) \nFormless (Canada) \n📍 Buddies in Bad Times Theatre \n🕖 7PM \nAll proceeds will be donated to Friends of Ruby\, supporting critical programs and services for 2SLGBTQIA+ youth. \nCelebrate trans visibility through film\, drag\, and community at the very first Formless Film Festival. 💖🎥 \n  \n The following content warnings are attached to the films: \n– Depictions or descriptions of verbal and/or physical violence \n– Depictions or descriptions of sexual violence or assault
URL:https://buddiesinbadtimes.com/event/formless-film-festival/
LOCATION:Tallulahs
END:VEVENT
